Configuration parameters common to Embedded and Discrete sync modes.

Field Documentation

UInt32 Vps_VipPortComConfig::ancChSel8b

For valid values see Vps_VipAncChSel8b.

UInt32 Vps_VipPortComConfig::clrAsyncFifoRd

'0' = Normal, '1' = Clear Async FIFO Read Logic.

UInt32 Vps_VipPortComConfig::clrAsyncFifoWr

'0' = Normal, '1' = Clear Async FIFO Write Logic.

UInt32 Vps_VipPortComConfig::ctrlChanSel

For valid values see Vps_VipCtrlChanSel.

UInt32 Vps_VipPortComConfig::enablePort

'0' = Disable Port, '1' = Enable Port. Keep 0 when doing setCfg, set to 1 using enablePort API.

UInt32 Vps_VipPortComConfig::expectedNumLines

Expected number of lines in the source.

UInt32 Vps_VipPortComConfig::expectedNumPix

Expected number of pixels per line in the source.

UInt32 Vps_VipPortComConfig::invertFidPol

FALSE: Keep FID as found, TRUE: Invert Value of FID.

UInt32 Vps_VipPortComConfig::pixClkEdgePol

For valid values see Fvid2_EdgePolarity.

UInt32 Vps_VipPortComConfig::repackerMode

Repacker Mode. Use Vps_VipRepackMode.
